quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare Гұaamon heen ko mbela-Й—on mbeltoron naatee damal ngal oЙ—on njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“ee moЖҙЖҙereeji
  2,59,TooГұЙ“e Й“ee mbayliti konngol ngol Й“e mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee lette sabu ko Й“e ngonno ko faasqeebe
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yimЙ“e mum ndiyam Min mbi'i fiyu haayre nde sawru maa ndu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e Й—iЙ—i puccitii heen yimЙ“e Й“ee fof keЙ“i yarde, Гұaamee njaree e njeЙ—u Alla taa mbaЙ—ee bonannde dow lesdi ndi"
  2,61,"Nde mbii-Й—on aan Muusaa min min njondintaako e Гұaamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min puЙ—i lesdi gila e kappe e haakooji e buudi e Гұebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on njiЙ— lomtinde ko ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko, keЙ“on ko Й“uri jaasde Й—uum njippo-Й—ee Misara maa on keЙ“ ko tori-Й—on ko Й“e pawaa koyeera e woroЙ—de Й“e nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu Й“e njedduno aayeeje eЙ“e mbara AnnabaaЙ“e ko aldaa e goonga Й—uum noon ko goopi e tooГұe maЙ“Й“e"
